Bruce,

In reply to your asking if there&#39;s a problem, etc., I clearly heard 
a &quot;Yes&quot; and then something following that which I can&#39;t make out.

Thanks for posting some unlabeled EVPs.  I agree with you, if 
everyone, or most, people hear the same thing, then it&#39;s a general 
response meant to be public; otherwise, if only the researcher hears 
a particular remark, then it&#39;s most likely a personal EVP, meant for 
the researcher&#39;s ears alone.

Sharon

